00:15:23.999 --> 00:15:24.999
MAYBE NOT.

00:15:24.999 --> 00:15:26.999
IT'S NOT ONLY 
A CLIFF.

00:15:26.999 --> 00:15:28.999
THE CLIFF STICKS 
OUT AT THE TOP.

00:15:28.999 --> 00:15:32.999
Alda: 
THE ISLAND, CALLED DAPHNE MAJOR, 
IS ONLY A MILE OR SO ACROSS.

00:15:32.999 --> 00:15:34.999
FOR SOME QUARTER CENTURY NOW

00:15:34.999 --> 00:15:38.667
A TEAM OF BIOLOGISTS AND 
