00:15:52.125 --> 00:15:54.999
EVERY ONE OF THE FEW HUNDRED 
GROUND FINCHES

00:15:54.999 --> 00:15:56.999
THAT SHARE THIS LUMP 
OF VOLCANIC ROCK

00:15:56.999 --> 00:15:59.999
WITH LOW, RATHER SCRUBBY 
VEGETATION, SOME SEABIRDS

