IT'S A REALLY GREAT PLACE TO SEE 
EVOLUTION ACTUALLY HAPPENING

00:16:22.125 --> 00:16:24.999
BECAUSE THE SYSTEM, 
THE BIOLOGICAL SYSTEM, IS

00:16:24.999 --> 00:16:27.999
RELATIVELY SIMPLE: 
NOT TOO MANY COMPONENTS

