IS THAT THERE'S NO QUESTION

00:18:29.417 --> 00:18:31.999
THAT IT IS EVOLUTION HAPPENING 
IN FRONT OF OUR EYES.

00:18:31.999 --> 00:18:33.999
WE DON'T HAVE TO THINK 
OF EVOLUTION

00:18:33.999 --> 00:18:36.999
AS BEING SOMETHING THAT YOU 
ONLY GET FROM THE FOSSIL RECORD

00:18:36.999 --> 00:18:38.999
OR THEORIZING ABOUT IT.

00:18:38.999 --> 00:18:41.999
YOU CAN GO TO A PLACE LIKE 
DAPHNE MAJOR, WHERE IT'S SIMPLE

00:18:41.999 --> 00:18:44.999
AND YOU CAN ACTUALLY SEE 
EVOLUTION HAPPENING

00:18:44.999 --> 00:18:47.999
ALMOST ON A MONTHLY BASIS, 
BUT CERTAINLY AN ANNUAL BASIS.

